opinion:
538 U.S. 903

IN RE DISCIPLINE OF DANERI.
No. D-2349.

Supreme Court of United States.

March 10, 2003.

1

Edward Nicholas Daneri, of San Antonio, Tex., is suspended from the practice of law in this Court, and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
